Copy and paste all the code into a new `.html` file and open it in a web browser to see the virtual keyboard:

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Virtual Keyboard</title>
<style>
  body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
